{"data":[{"id":563763296,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2097a8b4740391cb861b7137a22b516a","url_token":"horizonmuber","name":"马康哲","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ba6752a31041746eb46ba3b03c3047f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6ba6752a31041746eb46ba3b03c3047f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2097a8b4740391cb861b7137a22b516a","user_type":"people","headline":"现役（蒟蒻）MOer","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":86,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563763296","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-bb0d3ab69ac789dd96f295d62f26630f_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546274021,"updated_time":1546279055,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":12,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e算了\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还是指出他真正的逻辑错误吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e搞数竞的人偶尔也会在证明里扩充定义\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以此处扩充-1是奇质数是没有什么大问题的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们来看看第一段证明\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0af185e3f898c224ee49186cd6fe15db_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4e7e0a70f3d010a7edf4a7a40118b517_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0af185e3f898c224ee49186cd6fe15db_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4e7e0a70f3d010a7edf4a7a40118b517_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0af185e3f898c224ee49186cd6fe15db_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0af185e3f898c224ee49186cd6fe15db_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e他先证明了：对于任意正整数n，2n∈B或2n=(-1)+(2n+1)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事实上这根本不用证明，因为后者是显然成立的.但在这个时候，\u003cb\u003e这个证明和我们玩了一个文字游戏，后者掺杂了一个条件：(2n+1)是质数.\u003c/b\u003e因而这个证明利用了这个隐含条件，草率导出哥猜.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这才是这个证明的根本错误.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我还疑心：这人是不是高一的，只是刚刚自学完选修2-1的简单逻辑就以为自己掌握了法宝，顺便和我们玩起了文字游戏.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其它情况的讨论错误一样.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd09601ef530e1cd8c96a0cb40aa3cab_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9ec4ce925213b5301af0fcb8473ca0ef_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd09601ef530e1cd8c96a0cb40aa3cab_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='540'%20height='960'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9ec4ce925213b5301af0fcb8473ca0ef_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd09601ef530e1cd8c96a0cb40aa3cab_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-dd09601ef530e1cd8c96a0cb40aa3cab_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zh